meanings: end, finish, close, be over, be done, be finished, be completed
a story with a happy ending

phrases.phrase: 오늘 진짜 정신 없네요. 난 정말 일이 안 끝나는 줄 알았어요.
meanings: 직장에서의 표현 This has been a bad day. I thought quitting time would never come.
실용회화-약속을 어겼을 때 I'll hurry over as soon as I'm finished.

meanings.meaning: not the end of the world
